CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOne of the 15-year-old boys was given
OL,12,Fa three-year youth rehabilitation
OL,13,Forder (YRO) with 180 days of intensive
OL,14,Fsupervision and surveillance for
OL,15,Fraping and taking indecent images of
OL,16,Fboth victims.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,FThe second boy received the same
OL,7,Fsentence for three charges of rape
OL,8,Fagainst each of the two victims and
OL,9,Ffour counts of taking indecent images
OL,10,Fby filming the incidents.
OL,12,FThe 14-year-old was given an 18-month
OL,13,FYRO for two charges of rape related to
OL,14,Fthe latter victim after encouraging
OL,15,Fthe second defendant, and for an
OL,16,Foffence of indecent images.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge
OL,7,FNicholas Rowland said the offences
OL,8,Fcommitted by the two 15-year-olds
OL,9,F"crossed the custody threshold", but
OL,10,Fhe should "avoid criminalising these
OL,11,Fchildren unnecessarily" and added that
OL,12,Fcustody was a "last resort".
OL,14,FJudge Rowland explained that although
OL,15,Fthe two 15-year-olds were assessed by
OL,16,FYouth Justice Services as "medium
OL,17,Frisk" of reoffending but "high risk of
OL,18,Fserious harm" to young females, he had
OL,19,Fto consider their backgrounds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,FHe said the first had been diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith ADHD and "long-standing anxiety"
OL,8,Fwhile the second had an IQ in the
OL,9,Fbottom 1%, had ADHD with "extreme
OL,10,Fneurodevelopmental impairment" and
OL,11,Fpresented "more like an eight-year-
OL,12,Fold".
OL,14,FBut the sentences attracted criticism,
OL,15,Fwith Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fsaying he found the case "distressing
OL,17,Fas a politician" and "as a father",
OL,18,Fand Lord Hermer stating that there was
OL,19,F"an epidemic of violence against women
OL,20,Fand girls in this country".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,FJazmine's family said in a statement
OL,7,Fahead of Wednesday's hearing that her
OL,8,Flife was "changed forever" by the
OL,9,Fattack and that they had "been forced
OL,10,Fto come before one of the highest
OL,11,Fcourts in the country simply to ask
OL,12,Fthat the seriousness of Jazmine being
OL,13,Fraped by two teenage boys is properly
OL,14,Frecognised".
OL,16,FThey said: "This is not only
OL,17,Fincredibly difficult for our family,
OL,18,Fbut deeply re-traumatising for
OL,19,FJazmine, who is once again being
OL,20,Frequired to relive the abuse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,F"Today's hearing is about far more
OL,7,Fthan Jazmine's case. It is about every
OL,8,Fsurvivor watching to see how the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system responds to
OL,10,Fthe devastating harm caused by rape.
OL,12,F"The outcome has the potential to
OL,13,Fshape not only Jazmine's future, but
OL,14,Fthe confidence that survivors across
OL,15,Fthe country have in a justice system
OL,16,Fthat they look to for protection.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,F"Whatever the court decides, we hope
OL,7,Fno survivor is left believing they
OL,8,Fmust suffer in silence or that seeking
OL,9,Fjustice is simply too great a burden
OL,10,Fto bear."
OL,12,FThe family are currently crowdfunding
OL,13,Fto establish a foundation to support
OL,14,Fother survivors of sexual violence
OL,15,Fnamed Stronger than Silence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782895707
OL,3,CRape victim says she 'will never be
OL,4,Cthe same' ahead of sentence review
OL,6,FBarrister Charlotte Proudman, founder
OL,7,Fof the law firm Proudmans representing
OL,8,FJazmine and other survivors of sexual
OL,9,Fviolence, said: "This appeal raises
OL,10,Fimportant questions about the criminal
OL,11,Fjustice system's response to the
OL,12,Flifelong impact of sexual violence for
OL,13,Fvictims.
OL,15,F"We remain committed to standing
OL,16,Falongside survivors and to driving
OL,17,Freform so that our family and criminal
OL,18,Fjustice systems protect, support and
OL,19,Fdeliver justice for victims."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
